cu.explanation_en: Setting GNB_PORT_FOR_S1U to 99999 (exceeds maximum port number) will cause invalid network interface configuration error and S1-U connection failure.

du.explanation_en: Setting prach_ConfigurationIndex to 200 (invalid value) will cause invalid PRACH configuration error and RACH procedure failure.
du.explanation_zh: 將 prach_ConfigurationIndex 設定為 200（無效值）會導致無效 PRACH 配置錯誤，並造成 RACH 程序失敗。
